## Hero flow for deploy-test

1. Load https://michaelwegter.com/demos/healthstack-patient-portal/
2. Click demo-fill button for patient creds OR type patient@healthstack.demo / DemoPatient123!
3. Click "Sign in securely" -- should land on Patient Dashboard (GET /dashboard/patient)
4. Click "Browse Providers" tab -- shows 4 provider cards (GET /services)
5. Click "Book Appointment" on any card -- opens slot picker
6. Click any time slot then "Confirm Appointment" -- calls POST /book, returns booking_id
7. Checkout page shows order summary -- click "Pay $XX.00" -- calls POST /checkout
8. Confirmation page shows green check + PaymentIntent ID (mock: pi_DEMO_...)
9. "View my dashboard" -- Patient Dashboard shows new booking with "Paid" status
10. Logout -- re-login as admin@healthstack.demo / DemoAdmin123!
11. Admin dashboard shows stat cards, audit log with new entries, PHI-minimized patient roster

If backend returns 404 on steps 3+, wait 30s and retry -- watcher restart in progress.
